m_Data.Description: Raw data from all channels including EEG, ECG and EMG if available

v_ChanNames.Description: Name of each channel in order according to rows in m_Data

d_sampleRate.Description: Sampling frequency (in Hz) of all the data in the recording, regardless of their type

v_sessionTimes.Description: Time in seconds of the beginning and ending of the music therapy intervention [beginning,ending]
